{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6fdf3aef7b","title":"中央关于团结一切在我国工作的外国同志为总路线和大跃进服务的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"47ac1d0741","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"6fdf3aef7b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"b2f26ff42e","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"6fdf3aef7b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指国务院外国专家局1959年8月26日整理的《苏联专家认为反右倾保守很好，希望能反彻底，并称赞中国人民干劲大》的材料。"},{"id":"c080550513","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"6fdf3aef7b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。林，指林彪，当时任中共中央副主席、国务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"36512d8770","type":"title","text":"中央关于团结一切在我国工作的外国同志为总路线和大跃进服务的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"6fdf3aef7b"},{"id":"b2f26ff42e","type":"paragraph","text":"此件“发给各有关部门和同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"6fdf3aef7b"},{"id":"c080550513","type":"paragraph","text":"要团结一切苏联专家同志及其他外国专家同志，和我们一道，反石倾，鼓干劲，争取超额完成任务。即便有少数人在一个时期和我们意见不一致，也应好好说服他们。总之，要遵照中央历次指示，好好团结一切在中国工作的外国同志，为总路线和大跃进服务。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"6fdf3aef7b"},{"id":"73c1235dc8","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"6fdf3aef7b"},{"id":"6a29bc5c95","type":"paragraph","text":"1959年9月4日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"6fdf3aef7b"},{"id":"d49bc11f8e","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、林、彭真阅后，尚昆办。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"6fdf3aef7b"},{"id":"816f59e825","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"6fdf3ae